Proper Form: Back flat against pad; deep depth.
Rear foot up; deep knee bend.
Drive elbows back; chest on pad.
Elbow out; strap up; deep stretch.
Arms back; curl w/o moving elbow.
Lie on side; raise to vertical.
Hold DB at chest; deep squat.
Chest to bar; palms face you.
Hook legs; lower to bottom chest.
Raise to side; slight elbow bend.
Standing; bar to chin; lock out.
Raise DBs all the way overhead.
